        <!-- What Is & How to Use -->
        <section class="what-is-section" style="margin: 3rem 0;">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>What Is a Random Key Generator?</h2>
                <p>A random key generator creates secure random sequences for passwords, API keys, security tokens, and other applications requiring unpredictable strings.</p>
                <p>This tool uses the Web Cryptography API for true randomness, suitable for security-sensitive applications.</p>
                
